trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representa um <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"> </xref> propriedade (e seu valor) de um componente de hardware ou software de sistema impressão.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> classe para a propriedade especificada.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attributeName` deve ser escrito exatamente como o nome de algum determinado <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>propriedade de um objeto do sistema de impressão, incluindo maiusculas e minúsculas.</xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Priority", not "JobPriority".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objeto deve ser escrito "Priority", não "JobPriority".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"> </xref> propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> representa.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> classe que tem o valor especificado para o atributo especificado.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attributeName` deve ser escrito exatamente como o nome de algum determinado <xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>propriedade de um objeto do sistema de impressão, incluindo maiusculas e minúsculas.</xref:System.Printing.PrintJobPriority>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Priority", not "JobPriority".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>objeto deve ser escrito "Priority", não "JobPriority".</xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> </xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Priority%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintJobPriority"></xref> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"></xref> represents.

trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor da propriedade que o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintJobPriorityProperty"> </xref> representa.
